.RS 4
This statement specifies how long to wait until retring the write_verify feature, if previous try was postponed, because the file was opened for writing at that time\&.
.sp
It\*(Aqs recommended to keep this value smaller enough than the write_verify_interval setting\&. The default value is 600 seconds (10 minutes)\&.
.sp
This parameter is only available in gfmd\&.conf, and ignored in gfarm2\&.conf\&. gfsd uses this setting at its startup by asking gfmd\&.
.sp
